Note on OpenFront.io

This project is an independent reimplementation of certain publicly
observable gameplay mechanics and numeric balancing found in openfront.io,
which is itself licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License v3.0
(AGPL-3.0).

No source code or art assets from openfront.io are included in this project,
and none were copied, translated, or ported into it. Gameplay rules,
mechanics, formula shapes, and numeric constants referenced during
development are facts and are not subject to copyright protection; only a
work's specific creative expression (source code, art, text) is protected.
All code in this repository is original expression with its own architecture,
naming, and documentation. AGPL-3.0 governs OpenFront's own expression — none
of which appears in this repository.

See docs/openfront-pr-plan.md for this project's licensing evaluation and
sourcing methodology.
